<h1>Hog Raising</h1>

<ol type=1><p>

<li>Visit five or more farms, and name and describe two (2) breeds of hogs found thereon; or attend an agricultural exhibition and describe the pedigree of one of the hogs shown at such exhibition.<p>

<li>Explain the different uses of hog products for both commerce and food.<p>

<li>Write out a balanced ration for fattening hogs, and give reason for its preparation.<p>

<li>Explain fully the symptoms of hog cholera, and the preventive measures in common use.<p>

<li>Name the different kinds of food rations needed for hogs from weaning time to marketing age.</ol>



